channel.title: [Macrosoft] FIXED: Browser Version 1b
channel.description:
Hello :), recently I made this browser and we have decided to publicly beta test it.
New link: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=DA1PQ4QS -----------------------------------------
If someone can please scan it so we get more downloads that would be nice :D
The browser uses IE technology with some firefox gui stuff etc. I made it real quick to see what I could do with it. If you guys have any suggestions please post them here. Bug reports would also be great :D[br][size=1]Posted at: August 06, 2006, 10:08:00 AM[/size][hr]I fixed the link.. cant believe i forgot to add the main DLL to the zip file :P
